179
00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:10.119
Don't just imitate.

180
00:07:10.440 --> 00:07:11.600
You have to change the style.

181
00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:13.440
Mr. Gu,

182
00:07:13.880 --> 00:07:15.200
