271
00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:35.440
Call me "senior" when
we're talking about pay.

272
00:11:36.760 --> 00:11:37.599
Senior.

273
00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:39.719
Please have red date tea.

274
00:11:43.799 --> 00:11:45.440
You are so young

275
00:11:45.679 --> 00:11:47.280
